Popular singer, Katy Perry has confirmed pregnancy rumors. The 35-year-old singer revealed her baby bump at the end of the music video for her new single Never Worn White’ on Thursday. Katy also expressed relief that she could stop hiding her baby bump on her Twitter page. She wrote: ‘Oh my God, so glad I don’t have to suck it in any more or carry around a big purse lol. “Let’s just say it’s gonna be a jam-packed summer.” She went ahead to reveal that her baby is due in the summer. This will be her first child with her 43-year-old fiancé Orlando Bloom. Perry who got engaged to Bloom on Valentine’s Day in 2019 is expected to get married this summer.